_sText:
You spawn on a wood platform, a trigger_hurt activates for the AFK people or stupid people who do not want to play. You have to make it to the top without dieing from a rock falling down on you. If you make it, you can get weapons and go through a teleporter and get a grenade with a crown stapped to it. You can push a button to kill the people below, kill them with your weapon, or wait and see if they die from the rocks!
